data.description: Welcome to your new home in North Crestview! This beautifully renovated (2010 Effective Date) 3-bdrm, 2-bath gem offers modern comfort and charm.As a military family-owned property, it's been meticulously maintained and loved. The spacious, fenced backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings and play.Inside, you'll find contemporary upgrades, including a tankless water heater for endless hot showers and a brand-new septic tank (March 2023) for worry-free living.This home is more than just a house; it's a place where memories are made. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!AC Unit Age: 2021 Roof Age: 2016NEW Fence & Gutters: 2021
